    FROM [Products] AS [p2]
    INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p.ProductCategory2] ON [p2].[CategoryId] = [p.ProductCategory2].[Id]
    ORDER BY [p2].[DateCreated] DESC, [p2].[Id]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [t2] ON [p.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[DateCreated] DESC, [t2].[Id]" (0723d8ff)

END, [p.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[TagId]
FROM [ProductTags] AS [p.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [t0].[DateCreated], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Id0], [p.ProductCategory.Products0].[Id] AS [Id1]
    FROM [Products] AS [p.ProductCategory.Products0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [p1].[DateCreated], [p1].[Id], [p.ProductCategory1].[Id] AS [Id0]
        FROM [Products] AS [p1]
        INNER JOIN [ProductCategories] AS [p.ProductCategory1] ON [p1].[CategoryId] = [p.ProductCategory1].[Id]
        ORDER BY [p1].[DateCreated] DESC, [p1].[Id], [p.ProductCategory1].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t0] ON [p.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t1].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t1].[DateCreated] DESC, [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1]" (0723d8ff)

        ORDER BY [p1].[DateCreated] DESC, [p1].[Id], [p.ProductCategory1].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t0] ON [p.ProductCategory.Products0].[CategoryId] = [t0].[Id0]
) AS [t1] ON [p.ProductCategory.Products.ProductTags].[ProductId] = [t1].[Id1]
ORDER BY [t1].[DateCreated] DESC, [t1].[Id], [t1].[Id0], [t1].[Id1]" (0723d8ff)
